{"tid":47218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大民研：自稱「香港人」比率下跌","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:14:23.000Z","uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd60d8c60ffa9af52b1186d768adc04d08170d87","tid":47218,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉及梁游宣誓風波後，港大民研發表最新的香港市民身分認同調查，發現香港市民自稱為「香港人」的比率下跌，由半年前調查的42%，下跌至35%。至於自稱「香港人」和「中國人」 混合身分（即「中國的香港人」或「香港的中國人」）之比率則上升9%至47%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，自稱是「中國人」的比率，較半年前的調查，微跌2%至16%（跌幅在誤差之內）。<br />\n<br />\n港大民研同時邀請受訪市民0至10分評分，測試市民對「香港人」及「中國人」等的身份認同感、重要度。今次調查發現，除了對「世界公民」身分的認同感和重要性評分變化不大外，巿民對其他五項身分的認同感和重要性評分都明顯回升。<br />\n<br />\n以0至10分絕對評分計，巿民對「香港人」的認同感為8.09分，較上次微升，其次是亞洲人（7.81分）、中華民族一份子（7.55分）、中國人（6.88分）、世界公民（6.76分）、中華人民共和國國民（6.25分）。與些同時，「香港人」是受訪港人視為重要度最高的身份。<br />\n<br />\n調查在本月12月至15日進行，當時中央政府已宣布，接受泛民主派成員申請回鄉證，梁振英已宣布不連任。"},{"pid":"4057dec5da12a78cac4538444d55bde6669c91af","tid":47218,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"地球人"},{"pid":"bbad7ac11b2fc2bf0ed4ca319a78aef3fbfbfb6d","tid":47218,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d858349b8a96d9c8e6521783538d7e11da7502f","tid":47218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"個調查係咪 天水圍做？"},{"pid":"8f9ab82c63b718753fe47683c6fc14350c002109","tid":47218,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"自認中國身分真係垃撚圾"},{"pid":"926f07b96d493e66ff84b557705244ed8bb64514","tid":47218,"uid":19119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"另一邊咁諗<br />\n係咪啫係愈來愈多強國人過咗嚟香港？"},{"pid":"9e433d6b7c185eb47e53805783eeb691a2a446ad","tid":47218,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"佢又係打屋企電話問？"},{"pid":"7ff80f0b53bc64a7ae0ddc33c5cf159eb453eb4d","tid":47218,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fac9257443d7bb4a30e41dee7b651ac6ec4ac18","tid":47218,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41a7a36df625be89007d6059722e7142376c181","tid":47218,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"港大民研結果都竟然咁,玩完.........."},{"pid":"bafa94b205ee4a56e49dbee06f6ee8377420b448","tid":47218,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"以前見到人講蝗語會笑人大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家一街細佬都係講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16a9f554565b9df285d89c4310786c1ce5ee201","tid":47218,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a968145a177aae18899dfa9d4c74bedb5cd4c5d","tid":47218,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"擺明個民調係高登做架LA~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facec1dc890305a0c1902c2424aaba8d340ff80c","tid":47218,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"另外，自稱是「中國人」的比率，較半年前的調查，微跌2%至16%（跌幅在誤差之內）。<br />\n<br />\n以0至10分絕對評分計，巿民對「香港人」的認同感為8.09分，較上次微升，其次是亞洲人（7.81分）、中華民族一份子（7.55分）、中國人（6.88分）、世界公民（6.76分）、中華人民共和國國民（6.25分）。與些同時，「香港人」是受訪港人視為